Definition: mechanism consisting of a system of rods and levers connected to the front wheels of a motor vehicle
Example: the steering gear pushes it left or right which swivels the front wheels, causing the vehicle to turn
Synonyms: mechanism, steering_system, p, consisting, of, a, system, rods, and, levers, connected, to, the, front, wheels, motor, vehicle, steering, gear, pushes, it, left, or, right, which, swivels, causing, turn
Category: noun.artifact
